{"case_id": "case-012-d6-23", "container": "HC2", "pipeline_depth": 6, "message": "CKD stage 4 (eGFR 22), osteoarthritis flare. Asking for ibuprofen 600mg TID.", "latency_ms": 5734, "llm_calls": 2, "tokens_in": 634, "tokens_out": 115, "cost_usd": 0.0001641, "task_success": true, "abstained": false, "answer": "Ibuprofen 600mg TID should be avoided in patients with CKD stage 4 due to the risk of accelerating renal decline. Preferred alternatives for pain management include acetaminophen or topical agents. (ckd_nsaid)", "tool_calls": 0, "hop_metrics": [{"hop": "vector_ingress", "latency_ms": 2, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "cache_gate", "latency_ms": 0, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "safety", "latency_ms": 2752, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 212, "tokens_out": 68, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "writer", "latency_ms": 2975, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 422, "tokens_out": 47, "tool_calls": 0}], "embed_count": 2, "cache_hit": true, "cache_score": 1.0, "variant": "novel", "error": null}
{"case_id": "case-008-d4-22", "container": "HC2", "pipeline_depth": 4, "message": "LDL 165, ASCVD 8%, no diabetes \u2014 initiate statin for primary prevention?", "latency_ms": 11376, "llm_calls": 2, "tokens_in": 255, "tokens_out": 208, "cost_usd": 0.00016305, "task_success": false, "abstained": false, "answer": "Given Clarithromycin's strong CYP3A4 inhibitory effect, co-administration with Simvastatin 40mg significantly increases Simvastatin plasma concentrations, elevating the risk of myopathy and rhabdomyolysis [1, 2].\n\n**Recommendation:**\nTemporarily discontinue Simvastatin 40mg for the duration of Clarithromycin therapy and for at least 7 days following the last dose of Clarithromycin [1, 3]. Advise the patient to report any muscle pain, tenderness, or weakness immediately. Simvastatin can be re-initiated 7 days after Clarithromycin discontinuation [1].\n\n---\n**Citations:**\n[1] Drug Information Database (e.g., Lexicomp, Micromedex, UpToDate).\n[2] Simvastatin Prescribing Information (e.", "tool_calls": 0, "hop_metrics": [{"hop": "vector_ingress", "latency_ms": 2, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "cache_gate", "latency_ms": 0, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "analyze", "latency_ms": 5706, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 107, "tokens_out": 39, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "writer", "latency_ms": 5663, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 148, "tokens_out": 169, "tool_calls": 0}], "embed_count": 2, "cache_hit": true, "cache_score": 1.0000001192092896, "variant": "paraphrase", "error": null}
